&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a Clinical Band 6 Sister/Charge Nurse on Ward 52. Ward 52 comprises of 38 beds for both trauma patients including NOF area and elective . A team leader, providing clinical leadership and management support, developing and evaluating best practice within the department. The post-holder will deputize for the department manager as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
